to use this widget

declare a widget as follow

NUM=new numpad(QWidget* parent); // parent is usuall the container of your numpad (e.g an empty widget of a .ui form)

// important members are

    float get_Value(); // to get the current value
    void clear_value(); // to clear the current value

//important signals are
    void value_changed(double); // to get notified when the value change

